    <section class="hero-main">
      <div class="container" id="main-content">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-sm-8">
            <h1>Get covered by DVA</h1>
            <p>DVA is simplifying the way it does business with clients. We need current and former members who enlisted
              after
              <strong>30 June 2004</strong> to help us test a new claims process.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-sm-4 ready-to-register">
            <button class="uikit-btn" onclick="window.location.href = '/unauth/registration'">Register</button> or
