      <h2>Veteran and family support services</h2>

      <div class="start-three">
        <div class="card summary-card medical">
          <div class="summary-card-content">
            <h3>
              <a href="medical-services">Medical services</a>
            </h3>
            <p>Access medical treatment and programs to help with accepted service related injuries or conditions.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card summary-card financial">
          <div class="summary-card-content">
            <h3>
              <a href="financial-support">Financial support</a>
            </h3>
            <p>Access financial support including income replacement and compensation for accepted service related injuries
              or conditions.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card summary-card councelling">
          <div class="summary-card-content">
            <h3>
              <a href="family-and-counselling">Counselling and family services</a>
            </h3>
            <p>Access individual, couple and family counselling, and group programs to help you and your family understand
              and address mental health concerns.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- start-three -->

      <div class="start-three">
        <div class="card summary-card household">
          <div class="summary-card-content">
            <h3>
              <a href="everyday-care">Everyday care</a>
            </h3>
            <p>Improve your daily life with services covering household needs, personal care, and home or vehicle modifications.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card summary-card career">
          <div class="summary-card-content">
            <h3>
              <a href="career-guidance">Career guidance</a>
            </h3>
            <p>Access rehabilitation programs to help your career post ADF including assistance with finding a job, career
              guidance, and worksite assessments to ensure your injury or condition does not affect you at work.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
